review: Dr Prerna mam is really v sweet , polite & a wonderful doctor. I was looking for a good skin doctor & I found clinic Eximus. I read really good reviews about Prerna mam on Google & I had visited her for consultation and even took my 1st session for face treatment the same day.  The staff is v well mannered , polite and always smiling. It was my 3rd session today & I can really see the difference. I highly recommend Clinic Eximus. Thank you Prerna mam & the entire team. Keep the good work &  thanks for great customer service The atmosphere in the clinic feels so homely , comfortable and nice. The first thing I notice was one lady coming out of the clinic & her face was glowing it was evident she took some face treatment while I was coming in the clinic. It was the first sign that told me I am in good hands. *** **** ***** ***** ****** *** ** **** *** ** *** **** ***** ******* *** *** **** ********* ***** ***** she is genuinely concerned about her patients and cares. She will suggest only what is best for us. She is the most humble, down to earth & kind soul I met.

review:
I went for a hair loss treatment, and in just 4 sittings, already seeing unbelievable results. My hair fall decreased steadily, bald patches started filing, and density improved. Overall results so far have been amazing. 

Thanks to Dr. Prerna and her team for helping me regain my lost confidence and tackling one of my biggest concerns for the past 5 years.

I was always under the impression that treatment is going to cost me a fortune, but I'm stunned with how reasonable the overall cost has been. 

Great experience overall.
